    "body": "This PR adds `custom_should_partition_ops: list[str]` to specify the name of custom ops upon which graph partition happens. It works with cache since it is a `list[str]` in the config file. The op name should be of format \"mylib::baz\".\r\n\r\nhttps://github.com/pytorch/pytorch/pull/166458 as original PR\r\n\r\n(cherry picked from commit bebabd7fce29ea49b9269aeaa9fe3f34a3e1127e)\r\n\r\nFixes #165341\r\n\n\ncc @voznesenskym @penguinwu @EikanWang @jgong5 @Guobing-Chen @XiaobingSuper @zhuhaozhe @blzheng @wenzhe-nrv @jiayisunx @ipiszy @chenyang78 @kadeng @muchulee8 @amjames @chauhang @aakhundov @coconutruben",
